{
  "id": "draw-steel-combat-tools",
  "title": "Draw Steel: Combat Tools",
  "description": "<p>Bringing the rules of Draw Steel to Foundry, one ability at a time.</p><p>Draw Steel: Combat Tools automates the combat mechanics of Draw Steel, including Forced Movement with full collision detection, Conditions (Frightened, Taunted, Bleeding, and more), Grab, Teleportation, NPC Death tracking, and class-specific ability automations. Each feature can be individually toggled in the settings, so you can use as much or as little of the module as fits your table.</p>",
